room_title: Escape room "Neutrino 42" by Boss-Play Escape Rooms in Oceanside
room_description: In a last ditch effort for freedom, the Reuleaux Rebellion has assigned you and your team to an undercover mission on an enemy prisoner transport ship: Neutrino 42! Can you escape your cryochamber imprisonment, intercept the enemy battle plans and end the evil reign of The Third Realm?
